title: Vegsource defends Durianrider, I defend myself (my response to "Nina and Randa's Dad", Jeff Nelson)
description:
Do you want to pretend that credible threats of gang violence within veganism (a group of goons beating someone down in the street) are equivalent to a misunderstanding (on video) about whether or not your (vegan) daughters eat honey-from-bees?  Really, my dude?
Here's the link to the earlier video (alluded to in this one) showing screen-shots of D.R.'s threats against me, in case you haven't seen it before: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CRLbgCzJHyM
